The '''Scientific Instrument Package''', sometimes called an '''SIP''' or '''Scientific Information Packet''' was a data collection and storage device.

During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], [[Jedi General/Legends|Jedi General]] [[Rii'ke En]] was sent to recover a SIP on the planet [[Honoghr/Legends|Honoghr]]. It contained data on the various viruses and strains created onboard the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Confederacy of Independent Systems]] research ship the ''[[Gahenna]]'', including the powerful defoliant [[Trihexalophine1138]].

